Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.60,0:00:08.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(370,571)}「约定」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.82,0:00:10.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨还没停呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.40,0:00:15.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是不放晴 和日向的约定就无法实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.91,0:00:17.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临 辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.49,0:00:19.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要受您照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.24,0:00:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穗香
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.83,0:00:23.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.67,0:00:25.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.96,0:00:27.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你走到哪了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.96,0:00:31.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一个山顶 TOMA之耳那里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:33.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍到好照片了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.84,0:00:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然因为下雨不怎么能看到好景色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.26,0:00:40.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍了些花和岩石
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.35,0:00:42.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍照真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.43,0:00:45.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 照相机也有别的使用方式哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.90,0:00:46.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思借我用下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.98,0:00:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰一下 可以帮忙照相吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.69,0:00:52.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.03,0:00:54.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.53,0:00:55.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都到一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.74,0:00:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来嘛来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.03,0:01:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我拍了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.08,0:01:02.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 茄子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.37,0:01:06.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.88,0:01:11.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我不怎么拍人 很新鲜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.22,0:01:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.10,0:01:20.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.14,0:01:21.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.56,0:01:25.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到能在这样的大山上面吃青花鱼 真厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.14,0:01:29.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 葵在富士山的时候没吃饭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.48,0:01:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵她啊 得了高山病 路上就倒下了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.57,0:01:35.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.40,0:01:38.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像这样哦 变成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.45,0:01:43.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别 别管我了 大家先走吧 噶啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.91,0:01:45.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那件事就不要再提了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.91,0:01:50.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 我没说过那样的话 噶啊是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.63,0:01:54.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧 穗香都笑话我了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.67,0:01:57.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.26,0:02:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平安爬上来了 太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.26,0:02:04.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:08.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.06,0:02:11.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这都多亏了我收到的礼物——鞋子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.61,0:02:15.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵 今天是几月几日呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.44,0:02:20.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么呢日向 今天不是8月11日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:22.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到8月11日呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.20,0:02:25.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到8月11日呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.66,0:02:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.08,0:02:31.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心夏 生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:38.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了今天 我烤了蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:42.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打工店里的薄先生告诉了我菜单
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.05,0:02:44.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.81,0:02:46.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穗香也要吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.18,0:02:49.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.48,0:02:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.40,0:03:00.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.78,0:03:02.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心夏 生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:04.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:56.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心夏看起来好困
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.09,0:03:58.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多该上去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.13,0:04:00.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:01.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 心夏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.26,0:04:09.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵的惊喜成功了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:11.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惊喜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:14.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实一直都很在意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:19.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三增峠的时候 葵有没有真的开心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.11,0:04:24.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向 你看起来无惧无畏的 意外心还挺细呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:29.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚才虽然也对穗香多管闲事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.83,0:04:32.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她看起来也不是完全不愿意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:35.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以一定可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.71,0:04:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得 笑容就是从一个人传递给另一个人的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:42.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信自己做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:45.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以日向也要相信自己 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:48.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.47,0:04:52.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实 我还有一件事很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.06,0:04:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:05:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 要是约定实现了 那之后会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.07,0:05:04.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是算了 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.24,0:05:11.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦马君和小群马
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要碰呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:18.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是今天拍的花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.54,0:05:20.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真美呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.34,0:05:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然晴天时候的花也很美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:26.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是下雨的时候又别有一番韵味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.38,0:05:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摄影可以把自己的视线如实的记录下来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:35.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后再看的时候就能想起那时在想些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.27,0:05:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.69,0:05:37.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:40.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天晴天就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:44.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说你有看日出的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:46.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 和日向的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:49.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那个最吵的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.41,0:05:53.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过呢 虽然我自己也觉得奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.70,0:05:58.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得实现约定有些不安呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.96,0:05:59.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不安？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.96,0:06:01.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉有什么要发生改变
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:06.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以来的我们 是不是会消失不见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:12.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直想拍的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.26,0:06:15.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算拍到了也不会结束
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为一定还会有别的想拍的景色出现
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:23.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想大概会一直继续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:26.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直继续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.86,0:06:29.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.28,0:06:35.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穗香 方便的话可以跟我交换邮件地址吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.12,0:06:39.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还想再和你聊天 也想看你的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.38,0:06:43.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登陆完成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.13,0:06:46.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,方便的话 下次也来饭能玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.05,0:06:49.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多该熄灯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天也要早起 睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.60,0:06:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:02.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:04.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.31,0:07:05.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.44,0:07:07.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.29,0:07:20.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一片漆黑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有风声和雨声
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天会晴天吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:30.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 葵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:34.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天会晴天吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.51,0:07:39.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 思考的东西是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:42.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.69,0:07:47.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 要是晴天就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.07,0:07:49.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:52.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:54.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.16,0:07:55.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.71,0:08:09.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:11.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.97,0:08:23.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨停了真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.31,0:08:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:26.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要雾再散了就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.65,0:08:29.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要登山
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.36,0:08:31.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:32.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:35.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不明白呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 只要继续爬下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定有一天就会知晓答案
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.87,0:08:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:47.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:15.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:18.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.46,0:09:35.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵你先说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.34,0:09:37.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向你先说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:42.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.76,0:09:43.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下山之后？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.27,0:09:47.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我想再去温泉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.56,0:09:49.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:53.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了很多事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.78,0:09:56.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.08,0:10:13.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天 我们俩再一起来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.88,0:10:14.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.21,0:10:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定 一定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.10,0:10:23.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:25.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.34,0:11:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算约定得以实现 那也并不意味着结束
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.31,0:11:10.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和日向 和大家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:14.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约定会一直继续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:32.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次去哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.83,0:11:34.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪儿都去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.17,0:11:41.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要想去 一定哪里都能去到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:51.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后也要制造很多很多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法忘记的回忆
